name: CoinDeal Token
description: CoinDeal Token is an ERC-20 utility token that will be tradable on multiple markets and pairs on the CoinDeal exchange. With CDL, users can lower their trading fees, vote for new coins, use CDL to trade on multiple markets, gain access to additional trading features, gain access to CoinDeal's social trading platform. Staking CDL Tokens in the CoinDeal wallet will allow decreasing trading fees to almost zero. Staking over 150.000 CDL will give a 0.0000% maker fee and a 0.0250% taker fee.
